# StableRoute frontend environment variables
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the values for your environment.
# Variables prefixed with `NEXT_PUBLIC_` are exposed to the browser bundle and must
# be safe to share (no secrets, no API keys). They are inlined at build time.

# Base URL of the StableRoute API backend.
# - In local development, the dashboard talks to a backend on `http://localhost:3001`.
# - In production, this must be a full absolute https:// URL pointing at your deployed backend.
# - The value is validated by src/lib/apiClient.ts: non-http(s) and malformed URLs
#   will cause the app to fail at module init rather than silently mis-routing.
NEXT_PUBLIC_STABLEROUTE_API_BASE=http://localhost:3001
